## Phase 1: Database Schema (Supabase + Sequelize Models)

### 1.1 Supabase Table: `college_branding`

This table stores the branding configuration for each college. Colleges without a row here will use the platform defaults.

| Column | Type | Default | Description |
|--------|------|---------|-------------|
| `id` | `INTEGER` (PK, auto-increment) | — | Primary key |
| `collegeId` | `INTEGER` (FK → `college.collegeId`, UNIQUE) | — | One branding per college |
| `primaryColor` | `VARCHAR(9)` | `'#43C17A'` | Main brand color (navbar bg, buttons, links) |
| `primaryDark` | `VARCHAR(9)` | `'#1E7745'` | Darker shade for hover states |
| `primaryLight` | `VARCHAR(9)` | `'#E6F9EF'` | Light tint for backgrounds/badges |
| `primaryForeground` | `VARCHAR(9)` | `'#FFFFFF'` | Text color on primary backgrounds |
| `secondaryColor` | `VARCHAR(9)` | `'#272372'` | Secondary accent (calendar, badges) |
| `secondaryForeground` | `VARCHAR(9)` | `'#FFFFFF'` | Text on secondary backgrounds |
| `accentColor` | `VARCHAR(9)` | `'#43C17A'` | Ring, scrollbar, selection highlight |
| `navbarBg` | `VARCHAR(9)` | `'#43C17A'` | Sidebar/navbar background |
| `navbarActiveBg` | `VARCHAR(9)` | `'#F4F4F4'` | Active nav item background |
| `navbarActiveText` | `VARCHAR(9)` | `'#43C17A'` | Active nav item text color |
| `navbarHoverBg` | `VARCHAR(20)` | `'rgba(80,214,137,0.3)'` | Nav hover overlay |
| `scrollbarThumb` | `VARCHAR(9)` | `'#43C17A'` | Custom scrollbar thumb color |
| `logoUrl` | `TEXT` | `NULL` | Optional custom logo URL |
| `faviconUrl` | `TEXT` | `NULL` | Optional custom favicon URL |
| `isActive` | `BOOLEAN` | `true` | Enable/disable custom branding |
| `createdAt` | `TIMESTAMPTZ` | `NOW()` | — |
| `updatedAt` | `TIMESTAMPTZ` | `NOW()` | — |
| `is_deleted` | `BOOLEAN` | `false` | Soft delete |
| `deletedAt` | `TIMESTAMPTZ` | `NULL` | Soft delete timestamp |

