## Phase 3: React Context — BrandingProvider

### 3.1 Create Branding API Helper

#### [NEW] `app/utils/context/branding/brandingAPI.ts`

Fetches the branding configuration from Supabase for a given `collegeId`.

### 3.2 Create Branding Context & Provider

#### [NEW] `app/utils/context/branding/useBranding.tsx`

This context:
1. Reads `collegeId` from the user's existing context (admin, faculty, student, etc.)
2. Fetches the branding row from `college_branding`
3. Applies all CSS variables to `document.documentElement.style`
4. Falls back to defaults if no custom branding exists
5. Provides a `branding` object for JS-level access (e.g., AG-Charts fill colors)

