## Phase 4: Gradual Migration of Hardcoded Colors

> [!WARNING]
> This is the largest phase. There are **600+ occurrences** of `#43C17A` alone across the codebase. We will migrate in **batches by portal**, not all at once.

### 4.1 Migration Strategy — Replacement Map

| Hardcoded Value | CSS Variable | Tailwind Class |
|----------------|-------------|---------------|
| `bg-[#43C17A]` | `var(--brand-navbar-bg)` | `bg-[var(--brand-navbar-bg)]` |
| `text-[#43C17A]` | `var(--brand-primary)` | `text-[var(--brand-primary)]` |
| `text-[#1E7745]` | `var(--brand-primary-dark)` | `text-[var(--brand-primary-dark)]` |
| `bg-[#43C17A1C]` | — | `bg-[color-mix(in_srgb,var(--brand-primary)_11%,transparent)]` |
| `bg-[#272372]` | `var(--brand-secondary)` | `bg-[var(--brand-secondary)]` |
| `hover:bg-[#50D689]/30` | `var(--brand-navbar-hover-bg)` | `hover:bg-[var(--brand-navbar-hover-bg)]` |
| JS: `fill: "#43C17A"` | Read from context | `const { branding } = useBranding(); fill: branding.primaryColor` |

### 4.2 Migration Order (By Portal Priority)

| Batch | Portal | Estimated Files | Priority |
|-------|--------|----------------|----------|
| 1 | **Navbars** (all 13) | ~13 files | 🔴 Highest — most visible |
| 2 | **College Admin** portal | ~30 files | 🔴 High |
| 3 | **Admin** portal | ~25 files | 🟡 Medium |
| 4 | **Faculty** portal | ~40 files | 🟡 Medium |
| 5 | **Student** portal | ~50 files | 🟡 Medium |
| 6 | **Parent** portal | ~15 files | 🟢 Lower |
| 7 | **Finance / HR / Placement** | ~30 files | 🟢 Lower |
| 8 | **Shared Utils** (table, card, etc.) | ~20 files | 🟢 Lower |
| 9 | **Profile** module | ~25 files | 🟢 Lower |

### 4.3 Example: Navbar Migration (Batch 1)

**Before** (hardcoded):
```tsx
<div className="bg-[#43C17A] flex flex-col ...">
  <Link className={`${isActive ? "text-[#43C17A]" : "text-white"}`}>
```

**After** (dynamic):
```tsx
<div className="bg-[var(--brand-navbar-bg)] flex flex-col ...">
  <Link className={`${isActive ? "text-[var(--brand-navbar-active-text)]" : "text-white"}`}>
```

### 4.4 Example: AG-Charts Migration (JS Colors)

**Before**:
```tsx
const options = { series: [{ fill: "#43C17A" }] };
```

**After**:
```tsx
const { branding } = useBranding();
const options = { series: [{ fill: branding.primaryColor }] };
```

