## Phase 6: Caching & Performance

### 6.1 Client-Side Caching
- Cache branding in `localStorage` with a TTL of 24 hours
- On login, check cache first → if fresh, apply instantly (zero flicker)
- If stale or missing, fetch from DB → update cache

### 6.2 SSR Considerations
- CSS variables with defaults in `:root` ensure SSR renders correctly with default branding
- Client-side hydration then overrides with college-specific values
- No FOUC (Flash of Unstyled Content) because defaults match the current look

